data.title: Tengtou Tourist Area, Tengtou Village, Ningbo
data.meta_description: Xikou-Tengtou Tourist Area is famous for Xuedou Mountain, known as hometown of Chiang Kai-Shek, and a destination to experience China rural life.
data.text:
Admission Fee CNY 120 for the Native Place of the Chiang Family

CNY 120 for Xuedou Mountain

CNY 30 for transportation fee on Xuedou Mountain

CNY 65 for Shangliangang Hill

CNY 80 for Tengtou Village

CNY 180 for the Native Place of the Chiang Family and Xuedou Mountain; the ticket is valid for 2 days. Opening Hours The Native Place of the Chiang Family:

April-October: 7:45 - 17:30; November-March: 7:45 - 17:00

Xuedou Mountain:

April-October: 8:10 - 17:10; November-March: 8:10 - 16:40

Xufu Rock:

April-October: 8:30 - 16:50; November-March: 8:30 - 16:20

Shanglianggang Hill: 8:30 - 16:30

Tengtou Village: 7:00 - 17:00
